sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client Application
    participant EnvoyGW as Envoy Gateway
    participant EPP as llm-d EPP (ext-proc)
    participant KVCache as llm-d KV-Cache
    participant vLLM1 as vLLM Pod 1
    participant vLLM2 as vLLM Pod 2
    participant OTEL as OTEL Collector

    Note over Client,OTEL: Workflow 3: LLM Inference with llm-d Scheduling

    Client->>EnvoyGW: POST chat/completions (HTTPS/443)
    EnvoyGW->>EPP: ext_proc: route request (gRPC/9002, TLS 1.2+)

    EPP->>KVCache: Query KV-cache hit rates (gRPC/8300)
    KVCache-->>EPP: Cache scores per endpoint

    EPP->>EPP: Score endpoints by KV-cache prefix hit, queue depth, load balance

    alt vLLM Pod 1 has best KV-cache hit
        EPP-->>EnvoyGW: Route to vLLM Pod 1
        EnvoyGW->>vLLM1: Forward request (HTTP/8000)
        vLLM1->>vLLM1: Process inference (GPU compute)
        vLLM1-->>EnvoyGW: Completion response
    else vLLM Pod 2 selected
        EPP-->>EnvoyGW: Route to vLLM Pod 2
        EnvoyGW->>vLLM2: Forward request (HTTP/8000)
        vLLM2->>vLLM2: Process inference (GPU compute)
        vLLM2-->>EnvoyGW: Completion response
    end

    EnvoyGW-->>Client: Chat completion response (HTTPS)

    EPP->>OTEL: Export trace spans (OTLP gRPC/4317)
